Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.14,0:00:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜 小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.77,0:00:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期一再见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.19,0:00:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.49,0:00:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.41,0:00:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你每次都这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.41,0:00:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.65,0:00:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 一边去 我要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.84,0:00:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要打工吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.18,0:00:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.10,0:00:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 小鸠 辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.53,0:00:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 有什么我能帮忙的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.14,0:00:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.59,0:00:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.04,0:00:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(兼职 招聘信息)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.91,0:01:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈啊

