Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.48,0:02:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[...侦探 花户小鸠.]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.16,0:02:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.03,0:02:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来兼职有这么多种类啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.75,0:02:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种书借来干什么...啊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.19,0:02:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是要兼职啦 像藤本先生一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想帮忙还一点借款么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.26,0:02:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.50,0:02:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如在清爽的早晨送报纸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.92,0:02:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是睡懒觉的你去送?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃...那么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如为大家送披萨到家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.49,0:03:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你绝对会迷路的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.56,0:03:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃...那...那么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.43,0:03:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如帮忙搬家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.08,0:03:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬运瓶瓶罐罐的时候大概会搞砸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.92,0:03:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜 那要兼怎样的职才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别问我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.68,0:03:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.88,0:03:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.39,0:03:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 弄破了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.01,0:03:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.99,0:03:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 缝好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.63,0:03:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:03:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 还有一件事想拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.48,0:04:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 借伞的那位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.75,0:04:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那个时候的...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.07,0:04:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前承蒙照顾 谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 你们认识啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.57,0:04:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 自我介绍一下 我是店长植田
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是花户小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠小姐是在我的公寓里住的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.52,0:04:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时在艾草保育园帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.15,0:04:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说想找个可以兼职的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就想起这家店了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.22,0:04:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果周末店里很忙的时候能来帮忙的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.73,0:04:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.28,0:04:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我的手治好为止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.42,0:04:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是这种状态
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...我其实很冒失的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是前两天弄伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.34,0:04:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过忙起来的时候 店长太辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.20,0:04:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照 小鸠小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.17,0:05:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 也请您多关照 店长先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.98,0:05:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.29,0:05:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫大村裕美 请多关照 小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.44,0:05:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么加油吧 小鸠小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.53,0:05:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我换好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.73,0:05:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈 太好了 制服很合适呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.32,0:05:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我做什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,0:05:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先客人来了的话 要说"欢迎光临"欢迎光临!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.28,0:05:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就...就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.21,0:05:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后问客人要买什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问好把蛋糕装进那个盒子里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.11,0:05:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收银机我来操作 收钱以后...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.73,0:05:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说"谢谢惠顾"是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.17,0:05:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.97,0:05:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.19,0:05:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.65,0:06:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 先试一试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.10,0:06:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我要草莓蛋糕和勃朗峰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.86,0:06:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝士蛋糕...不对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.73,0:06:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草莓蛋糕 勃朗峰 奶酪...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苹果?柠檬?呃...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.49,0:06:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要奶油泡芙 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.23,0:06:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草莓蛋糕和勃朗峰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.33,0:06:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苹果派加柠檬派和奶油泡芙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太厉害了 裕美小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.00,0:06:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠 把它们装进盒子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...是!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.21,0:06:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...草莓蛋糕和... 哇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.44,0:06:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镇定一点 另取一块吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.68,0:06:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.81,0:06:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后是勃朗峰和...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.69,0:06:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苹果派和柠檬派 奶油泡芙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 最后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.55,0:07:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.14,0:07:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 活泼的店员小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 习惯了就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.07,0:07:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.54,0:07:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满里奈和妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.94,0:07:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠是蛋糕店员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 今天是蛋糕店员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.07,0:07:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要什么蛋糕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.78,0:07:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我们来取满里奈的生日蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.30,0:07:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 今天你生日啊 生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.43,0:07:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠 帮她装起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.45,0:07:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.22,0:07:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.31,0:07:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:07:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.13,0:08:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了 小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.13,0:08:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.12,0:08:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.79,0:08:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.65,0:08:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.21,0:08:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(满里奈 生日快乐)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿错蛋糕了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶!?我去追满里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.42,0:08:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满里奈!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.04,0:08:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.00,0:08:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.75,0:08:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请给我那个和这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.67,0:08:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.56,0:08:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠 这位客人是要勃朗峰和芝士蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.07,0:08:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.39,0:08:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 这是礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:08:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百祗先生会很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.84,0:09:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表是个布偶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天也拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.70,0:09:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗?明天再来也可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.37,0:09:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 当然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.14,0:09:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕美你也可以回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.35,0:09:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 整理工作还没有做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.60,0:09:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的伤还没有好 不要勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.47,0:09:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么店长我先回...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.14,0:09:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?没...没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.16,0:09:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过看上去裕美小姐好像在担心着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:09:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长有点让人担心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.00,0:10:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去好像有什么烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.06,0:10:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然问过他一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他却说"没什么"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.57,0:10:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.33,0:10:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店的生意也有条不紊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.41,0:10:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么店长是为什么烦恼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是欠债?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.96,0:10:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾草保育园正为这个焦头烂额呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠难道是为此才在这里兼职的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.20,0:10:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.46,0:10:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...我不算什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老师和藤本先生才了不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.47,0:10:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我想要是能够出上一点力就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想出点力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.92,0:10:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为店长...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.36,0:10:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃啊这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.51,0:10:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想帮忙却帮不上忙的话是很痛苦的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.29,0:11:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去调查看看店长的烦恼到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.33,0:11:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不要做多余的事情然后被炒鱿鱼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.90,0:11:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然这么好吃的蛋糕就吃不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 但是还可以去其他各种地方打工嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.76,0:11:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寿司店
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤肉店
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高级中华料理店
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.18,0:11:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠...接下来打算在哪里打工?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.44,0:11:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然还是继续去蛋糕店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.31,0:11:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.93,0:11:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.60,0:11:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.73,0:11:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能帮我把这些曲奇放到货架上吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.23,0:11:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.13,0:11:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.49,0:11:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才 店长是不是对我叹了一口气?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:12:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道店长所烦恼的事 与我有关?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去问问店长到底有什么烦心事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.11,0:12:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.42,0:12:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.50,0:12:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么能不能若无其事地帮我问问?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.48,0:12:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 小鸠加油了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.01,0:12:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.73,0:12:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.78,0:12:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 其实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我有事要若无其事地问问您!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:12:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.64,0:13:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?什么事情?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.22,0:13:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长是不是有什么烦恼的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.96,0:13:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 什么事情都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.21,0:13:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 裕美小姐说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.20,0:13:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您经常若有所思地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什么话欲言又止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.77,0:13:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,样子很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实裕美不用担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.75,0:13:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.02,0:13:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一说更觉得放心不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.82,0:13:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.13,0:13:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 小鸠?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.05,0:13:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.61,0:13:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么在这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.03,0:13:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠会在这里帮忙一直到我的伤痊愈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.74,0:13:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您来买蛋糕吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.70,0:13:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正要去千岁家玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.14,0:13:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想带些手信去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.11,0:13:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是久违了呢 chiroru的蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得您曾经为您丈夫订过生日蛋糕的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:13:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.13,0:14:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老师的丈夫...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说结婚了有老公
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.41,0:14:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是从来没有看到过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.14,0:14:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就可能离婚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老师看上去很寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事 可不能直接问哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.45,0:14:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.91,0:14:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都有不想说的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.27,0:14:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不都瞒着大家为了保育园去打工的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都一样 并不是什么都该说出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.41,0:14:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,chiroru的店长也是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.25,0:14:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.27,0:14:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是裕美小姐很想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.13,0:14:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候到底要怎么做才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.04,0:14:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 比如悄悄地调查之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.68,0:14:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我可不认为这是土鸠能胜任的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.15,0:15:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢光临
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.20,0:15:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还算得上是悄悄地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.98,0:15:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.18,0:15:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.82,0:15:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在悄悄地调查呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.53,0:15:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.93,0:15:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像侦探一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侦探?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.12,0:15:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 原来这就是侦探啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.04,0:15:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要调查很多东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.21,0:15:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动机啊 不在场证明 证据之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.19,0:15:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有搜查啊 听取证言 跟踪什么的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.05,0:15:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅 我们也要帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.60,0:15:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 侦探是独自行动的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像偏离方向了吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.09,0:15:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.13,0:16:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.98,0:16:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我今天是侦探
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.13,0:16:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侦探...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.35,0:16:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,chiroru里有没有什么不正常的?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 没有吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.39,0:16:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 是不是发生了什么事件..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是店长烦恼事件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长他吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.57,0:16:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在烦恼?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有什么线索呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.78,0:16:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 就算你问我们也...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没有什么吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.62,0:16:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,chiroru的蛋糕很有人气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.03,0:16:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是工作以外的事情吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.08,0:16:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.56,0:16:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.52,0:16:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...那我们就先走了...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.86,0:16:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要陪你玩这种游戏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用我自己的搜查网
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.58,0:16:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜查网?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.83,0:16:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪能接受那种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.36,0:16:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真小气啊 玄琥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.10,0:16:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要商量恋爱方面的事 你还是找别人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.21,0:16:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那今天就这样把手信带回去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.64,0:17:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你只是想过来白吃年轮蛋糕的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.53,0:17:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是生气了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.82,0:17:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.82,0:17:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕美小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.17,0:17:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.52,0:17:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做侦探
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.06,0:17:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今知道的只有chiroru的蛋糕很受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以烦恼的原因在工作以外
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.29,0:17:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是店长他总是送小孩子巧克力做赠品
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.79,0:17:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会注意别人的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.27,0:17:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了大家都很喜欢店长做的蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.73,0:17:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也收到巧克力了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长对大家都很友善呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.60,0:17:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕美小姐 现在开始要跟踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.78,0:17:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠 算了吧 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.82,0:18:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.61,0:18:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和谁有约吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.26,0:18:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷跟在后边是不对的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.31,0:18:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好像有人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.52,0:18:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不认识吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.56,0:18:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不认识
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说是约会?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.11,0:18:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会不对我说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.38,0:18:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点 裕美小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被店长发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.30,0:18:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕美?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.21,0:18:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕美小姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.96,0:19:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕美小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.18,0:19:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.64,0:19:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.10,0:19:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.23,0:19:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.47,0:19:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.01,0:19:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.91,0:19:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 刚刚和店长见面的那位是?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.61,0:19:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是面试...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.94,0:19:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备新收的兼职的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兼职?为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然周末小鸠会来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.71,0:19:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一直不能让裕美你好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.31,0:19:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.51,0:19:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你会不会是太累了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.33,0:19:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 会受伤是不是也因为这个原因
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.68,0:19:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.25,0:19:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 就是在烦恼这件事?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.63,0:19:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.39,0:19:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕美真的做的非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.63,0:19:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我则是太依赖你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.32,0:19:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以觉得很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.10,0:20:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会 我和店长一起工作觉得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算没有休假也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.78,0:20:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天接触那些因为蛋糕而高兴的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.63,0:20:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有和店长一起让我觉得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.09,0:20:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.38,0:20:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会受伤是因为...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.58,0:20:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是裕美...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.17,0:20:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.51,0:20:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些伤是在练习做蛋糕的时候弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想哪怕能多帮店长一点也好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.61,0:20:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就学着...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.82,0:20:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我瞒着你真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.04,0:20:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能吃吃看吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.84,0:21:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.22,0:21:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.16,0:21:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且新的兼职的人也要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.35,0:21:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有空的时候一起学习做蛋糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.53,0:21:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.41,0:21:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛解决掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.82,0:21:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 小鸠侦探解决掉事件了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.42,0:21:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长是因为想让裕美休息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.52,0:21:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而裕美则是想能更好地帮助店长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.87,0:21:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人都在为对方着想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.68,0:21:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样一个美好的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.58,0:21:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.13,0:21:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正又吃到年轮蛋糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.50,0:21:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个蛋糕不是chiroru的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.84,0:21:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且以前也作为手信带回来过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.90,0:22:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道和五百祗先生的搜查网有什么关系哦 对了 这次的分数
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.88,0:22:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为吃到了蛋糕所以满分一百分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.46,0:22:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.19,0:22:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.33,0:22:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.26,0:22:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是手信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.88,0:22:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我兼职的店里的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.11,0:22:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兼职?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.48,0:22:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.82,0:22:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.34,0:22:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以藤本先生就多点休息 多点去学校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.29,0:22:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 就算你努力也没什么用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.23,0:22:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺负人...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.92,0:22:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.30,0:22:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太勉强了把自己弄病了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.16,0:22:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说这是在担心我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.64,0:22:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.54,0:22:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.01,0:22:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那个还是去把脸上的涂鸦弄掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.66,0:22:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是一百分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.02,0:22:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么的 那是涂鸦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.94,0:22:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是 藤本先生太欺负人了只给五十分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.57,0:22:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道你说啥...

Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.06,0:24:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}[...银色之瞳.]

Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.08,0:23:07.72,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}人はみな飛んでみたいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.89,0:23:15.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}重力に騙されてるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.34,0:23:23.25,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}誰もほんとは飛べるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.40,0:23:32.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}あの子があんなに悲しそうなのは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.67,0:23:42.65,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}自分の影をどこかに忘れてきちゃったからかも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.95,0:23:45.26,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}それなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.58,0:23:49.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}ありがとうって　君に言えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.78,0:23:53.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}ありがとうって　君が笑えば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.81,0:24:01.00,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}いったりきたり　嬉しくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.37,0:24:05.75,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}君が幸せになる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.98,0:24:10.17,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}心配なんていらないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.34,0:24:14.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}一緒にいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.04,0:24:27.34,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}嬉しくても涙が出るなんて不思議だ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.98,0:23:07.62,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}明明人们都是那么想飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.79,0:23:15.05,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}只不过被重力所欺骗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.24,0:23:23.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}其实谁都可以在天上翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.30,0:23:32.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}那个孩子为什么如此悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.57,0:23:42.55,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}也许是把自己的影子忘在了哪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.85,0:23:45.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}是那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.48,0:23:49.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}如果能对你说 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.68,0:23:53.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}如果能看见你的笑容 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.71,0:24:00.90,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}来来往往中 变得愉悦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.27,0:24:05.65,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}你一定能变得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.88,0:24:10.07,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}不需要担心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.24,0:24:14.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}因为我们在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.94,0:24:27.24,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}喜极而泣总是那么不可思议
